<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<sample sampleID="LBh9_00021" version="1.0" type="fixedLength">
<article articleID="LBh9_00021_F001">
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　壁<sampling type="start" />ぎわのオーディオにたたきつけられた彼を目で追った<ruby rubyText="しゅん">瞬</ruby><ruby rubyText="かん">間</ruby>、</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　あたしの<ruby rubyText="め">瞳</ruby>に、見慣れた後ろ姿が飛びこんできた。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　（え―…。）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　うそ。</sentence>
<sentence>まさか―…！？</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<blockEnd />
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「昴！？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<blockEnd />
<paragraph>
<sentence>　あたしの<ruby rubyText="さけ">叫</ruby>び<ruby rubyText="ごえ">声</ruby>に、その後ろ姿がふり返る。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　（あ…）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<blockEnd />
<paragraph>
<sentence>　―昴だった。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　あたしが、いちばん会いたかった男の子が、</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　今、<ruby rubyText="のぞ">望</ruby>んだままの夢のように、</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<blockEnd />
<paragraph>
<sentence>　あたしの前に、―立っていたんだ。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<titleBlock>
<title>
<sentence type="quasi">１５</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</title>
</titleBlock>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　（どうして…？）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　どうして昴が、ここにいるの―…？</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<blockEnd />
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「帰るよ！！</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">　りおさん」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　ボーゼンとするあたしに、昂が手をさしのべる。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　肩で息をしながら、<ruby rubyText="きび">厳</ruby>しい顔で。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「昴…？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「ちきしょ…、なんだよ、おまえは」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　突然の乱入者に気をのまれていた男の子達が、やっと<ruby rubyText="われ">我</ruby>に返って立ち上がる。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　最初に昂に<ruby rubyText="なぐ">殴</ruby>られた男の子が、くちびるの<ruby rubyText="はし">端</ruby>に血をにじませながら昂につかみかかった。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「ナメてんじゃねーよ！！</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">　てめえ…」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「昂…！！」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　―ガツッ！！</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　昴の<ruby rubyText="ほお">頰</ruby>に、男の子の<ruby rubyText="こぶし">拳</ruby>がきまる。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　メガネが<ruby rubyText="こわ">壊</ruby>れて吹っ飛んだ。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「昂！！」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　壁に手をついて<ruby rubyText="からだ">身体</ruby>を<ruby rubyText="ささ">支</ruby>えた昂は、顔を上げて相手をにらみつける。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　切れた目の<ruby rubyText="はし">端</ruby>から、血が流れだしてた。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　いつもの昂からは考えられないほど、<ruby rubyText="はげ">激</ruby>しい表情で、</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　昂が相手の男の子に飛びかかっていく。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<blockEnd />
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　―それからは、</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　もう、何がなんだかわからなかった。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<blockEnd />
<paragraph>
<sentence>　<ruby rubyText="なぐ">殴</ruby>り合いの<ruby rubyText="にぶ">鈍</ruby>い音。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　男の子達の<ruby rubyText="ど">怒</ruby><ruby rubyText="せい">声</ruby>。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　物の壊れる激しい音と振動。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　その中で、昂が…、</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　いつも<ruby rubyText="おだ">穏</ruby>やかで、やさし気な男の子が、メチャクチャに暴れてた。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　強気な<ruby rubyText="め">瞳</ruby>をして。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　別人みたいな激しさで。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　だけど、昂の相手は３人だった。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　しかも、多量のアルコールのせいで、理性なんか<ruby rubyText="な">失</ruby>くした…。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　疲れてきた昂の身体に、ひとりの<ruby rubyText="け">蹴</ruby>りが入る。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　フラついたところを、別のひとりが思いっきり殴りつけた。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「昂…っ！！」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　勢いよく<ruby rubyText="ゆか">床</ruby>に倒れた昂を、３人が何度も蹴りつける。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「やめて！</sentence>
<sentence>　やめてっ！！」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　あたしの<ruby rubyText="さけ">叫</ruby>びは、３人の耳には届いていないようだった。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　集団心理の<ruby rubyText="おそ">恐</ruby>ろしさ…？</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　３人は、よってたかって無抵抗の人間を痛めつけることを、おもしろがっているようだった。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　人間の、いちばん恐ろしい一面を、こんな時に見せつけられるなんて…。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<blockEnd />
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「やめて！</sentence>
<sentence>　お願い、死んじゃう！！」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　ガタン―！！</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　リーダー<ruby rubyText="かく">格</ruby>の男の子の腕にしがみついたけど、無言のままで突き飛ばされた。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　…ダメだ！！</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　このままじゃ、昴、ホントに殺されちゃう！！</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　どうしよう。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　どうしよう…？</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　（どうすればいい―！？）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<blockEnd />
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　その時、</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　男の子のひとりが、<ruby rubyText="なか">半</ruby>ば気を<ruby rubyText="うしな">失</ruby>いかけた昴に向かって、重たげなギターをふりあげた。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「昂…！！」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　もう、何も考えられなかった。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　頭の中がまっ白で。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　ただ、目の前に横たわる昂を、これ以上傷つけたくなかっただけ。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<blockEnd />
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「やめてーっ！！」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　<ruby rubyText="こん">渾</ruby><ruby rubyText="しん">身</ruby>の力をこめて叫んだ。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　その<ruby rubyText="しゅん">瞬</ruby><ruby rubyText="かん">間</ruby>、</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　自分でも、思ってもみなかったことがおこった。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<blockEnd />
<paragraph>
<sentence>　バリバリバリッ―！！</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<blockEnd />
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　突然、あたしの<ruby rubyText="からだ">身体</ruby><ruby rubyText="じゅう">中</ruby>から、</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　青白い<ruby rubyText="せん">閃</ruby><ruby rubyText="こう">光</ruby>がほとばしったんだ。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　（え―…？）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<blockEnd />
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　―</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　―…</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　部屋中のものをかき消すような、すさまじい光の<ruby rubyText="うず">渦</ruby>。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<blockEnd />
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　その光は、まるであたしの心のように、３人の男の子めがけて走り、</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　<ruby rubyText="つぎ">次</ruby>の瞬間、</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　三つの<ruby rubyText="からだ">身<sampling type="end" />体</ruby>が、まばゆい<ruby rubyText="せん">閃</ruby><ruby rubyText="こう">光</ruby>に包まれた。</sentence>
</paragraph>
</article>
</sample>
